eu.fbk.dkm.springles.base

Class ForwardingSpringlesRepository

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.collect.ForwardingObject
      • eu.fbk.dkm.springles.base.ForwardingSpringlesRepository
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SpringlesRepository, org.openrdf.repository.Repository

    public abstract class ForwardingSpringlesRepository
extends ForwardingObject
implements SpringlesRepository
    Implementation of SpringlesRepository that forwards by default all method calls to a delegate SpringlesRepository.

    This class is modelled after the 'forwarding' pattern of Guava (see ForwardingObject). Subclasses must implement method delegate() which is called by other methods and must provide the delegate SpringlesRepository instance.

    Note that this class does not implement the Sesame marker interface DelegatingRepository (it neither extends from RepositoryWrapper). It is up to subclasses to decide whether to implement that marker interface. In particular, note that implementing DelegatingRepository is mandatory if the subclass wants the delegate repository to be injected by Sesame as part of the initialization of a repository stack.
